      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that won't break the bank? This vehicle is ready for its next adventure! While it shows some expected signs of use and cosmetic wear from its time on the road, it remains a solid and functional choice for anyone seeking reliable transportation at a great value. It\u2019s a practical option that\u2019s eager to get back to work for its next owner!",
