    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable daily driver at an affordable price. Mechanically, the car is sound; it starts reliably, the engine runs consistently, and it handles reasonably well on the road. However, it does show its age with some visible wear and tear, including minor dings and scratches on the exterior and some fading on the interior upholstery. All major components are functional, but a buyer should expect the typical signs of use associated with a well-traveled vehicle.",
