      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present an exemplary specimen of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment, this unit represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection. Every mechanical component has been vetted to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for excellence.",
