    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in truly flawless condition\u2014it seriously looks and smells like it just left the dealership! Not a single scratch or dent to be found, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new but without that heavy new-car price tag, this is the one for you. Drop me a message, I\u2019d love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered here is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3, a pinnacle of the E46 chassis. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L straight-six, boasting a 7,900-RPM redline and crisp throttle response via individual throttle bodies. The drivetrain is anchored by a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension retains factory-spec kinematics with upgraded bushings for sharpened turn-in. Finished in pristine Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the aesthetic condition is commensurate with its mechanical excellence. A turnkey collector piece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2022 Sedan. Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. Full service history. No mechanical issues. Clean title.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in absolute showroom condition, this vehicle is a testament to meticulous ownership and represents a rare find for the discerning collector. The exterior features a flawless factory paint finish with a deep, mirror-like luster, free of any stone chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. It has been professionally detailed and treated with a high-end ceramic coating to preserve its pristine aesthetic. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather remains supple with no signs of wear, and every surface is free of dust or scuffs. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been maintained strictly according to manufacturer schedules at authorized service centers with full documentation provided. All electronic systems, from the high-fidelity audio to the advanced driver assists, function with precision. This vehicle has been stored in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. If you are seeking a specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line, this is the unparalleled choice.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
